{"tid":1651680,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"[求解簽]赤松黃大仙指點迷津","createTime":"2019-10-13T12:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T16:37:47.000Z","uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"eced5729d20e4db196f78b77dd3e7867a03a3e4d","tid":1651680,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:11:11.000Z","msg":"最近就同屋企人去求簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問下大仙到底示威者可唔可以平平安安咁贏呢場革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後大仙就話<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/13/200735_65bf5bfb50dd7d8b96eaf007051b4eec.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F13%2F200735_65bf5bfb50dd7d8b96eaf007051b4eec.jpeg&h=829638d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係個解簽佬就好hea咁講翻鍾馗個故事同埋講左句贏唔係唔得，不過好難就算。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我同屋企人都覺得呢枝簽其實係好嘢，只不過個解簽佬係藍屍所以唔講，所以我想問下有冇人識解。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5fcd226e440932fa1ecc4d1c91d4245467ecea3","tid":1651680,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:11:33.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"bffbc406972d812f19aa306a51f8c40879f911f3","tid":1651680,"uid":312125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:14:11.000Z","msg":"我嘅解讀係有殉國義士會協助香港人成功<br />\n<br />\n【以正視聽】已FC！今日割頸嘅係中共特務嫁禍示威者所為，早前連登巴打已預告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1651683</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3537729dcf349827101f2142fc680797718d0d04","tid":1651680,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fs9nvNd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffs9nvNd.jpg&h=141b52ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veF1TV.jpg\" data-thumbna